    riskFactors: ["Polypharmacy increasing interaction risk", "Genetic predisposition (HLA-B*5801 for allopurinol SJS, HLA-B*1502 for carbamazepine SJS in Asians)", "Multiple serotonergic medications", "High-dose or rapid antipsychotic initiation (NMS)", "Hepatic or renal impairment", "Prior ADR history", "Slow CYP metabolizer status"],
